text: Toysa atu ama tamiray batayah yanik akumaay, ama qunxa weeqaytih leek aqubaay ama baxat inti wagrisaay ruffu kaat ixxic; tokkel sinaamak numuk teyna tubleeh, tokkel usuk atu xalte baxih xaagu kok abek, toysa diggah anu racmaan kinni rabbih tibbi axcem axbuuxuh innil hee kaak ixxic, (nadri kinnuk) asaaku inkinnah seehadaytu luk yaabe waamah
